**MACRO/MARKETS:** Robotics automation accelerates capex cycles across manufacturing and logistics; embedded reasoning reduces deployment friction, supporting multi-year secular growth in industrial automation—material for EM supply chains and energy-intensive sectors facing labor scarcity.

**CREDIT RISK:** No direct IFRS 9/ECL impact; monitor robotics capex financing cohorts for collateral valuation (depreciation curves) and refinancing risk if adoption spreads faster than balance-sheet recovery in mid-market industrials.

**AI/ML:** Spatial reasoning + multi-view fusion mirrors banking's emerging need for synthetic data validation in fraud detection and collateral imaging (mortgage/asset-backed lending);
